POST {{ExpenseTracker_Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "Test123!"
}


### Login user
POST {{ExpenseTracker_Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "Test123!"
}

